hh3chipsNegotiateSaMode.name: hh3chipsNegotiateSaMode

hh3chipsExpBytes.name: hh3chipsExpBytes

hh3chipsSoftBytes.name: hh3chipsSoftBytes
hh3chipsSoftBytes.description: This object specifies the lifetime in bytes of the tunnels generated using this policy specification.

hh3chipsExpTimeout.name: hh3chipsExpTimeout
hh3chipsExpTimeout.description: This object specifies the lifetime in seconds of the tunnels generated using this policy specification.

hh3chipsSoftTimeout.name: hh3chipsSoftTimeout
hh3chipsSoftTimeout.description: This object specifies the lifetime in seconds of the tunnels generated using this policy specification.

hh3chikeSATable.description: The table containing IKE SA entities configured on NDEC by the operator.

hh3chikeSAEntry.name: hh3chikeSAEntry
hh3chikeSAEntry.description: Each entry contains the attributes associated with a single IKE SA entity.

hh3chikeConnId.name: hh3chikeConnId
hh3chikeConnId.description: The identifier of IKE SA connection.

hh3chikePeerIpAddr.name: hh3chikePeerIpAddr
hh3chikePeerIpAddr.description: The peer IP address of this IKE SA.

hh3chikePhase.description: The phase of this IKE SA.

hh3chikeDoi.description: The domain of this IKE SA

hh3chipsIKEPolicyTable.name: hh3chipsIKEPolicyTable
hh3chipsIKEPolicyTable.description: List of all ISAKMP policy entries.

hh3chipsIKEPolicyEntry.name: hh3chipsIKEPolicyEntry
hh3chipsIKEPolicyEntry.description: Each entry includes the properties of a ISAKMP Policy entry.

hh3chipsIsakmpPolEncr.name: hh3chipsIsakmpPolEncr
hh3chipsIsakmpPolEncr.description: The specified encryption transform. It is used by Internet Key Exchange(IKE) tunnels to protect the ISAKMP PDUs.

hh3chipsIsakmpPolHash.name: hh3chipsIsakmpPolHash
hh3chipsIsakmpPolHash.description: The specified hash transform. It is used by Internet Key Exchange(IKE) tunnels to protect the ISAKMP PDUs.

hh3chipsIsakmpPolAuth.name: hh3chipsIsakmpPolAuth
hh3chipsIsakmpPolAuth.description: The specified peer authentication method. The local entity would authenticate the peer using the method specified by this object when this policy entity is selected to negotiate with a peer.

hh3chipsIsakmpPolGroup.name: hh3chipsIsakmpPolGroup
hh3chipsIsakmpPolGroup.description: This object is used to specify the Oakley group which is used for Diffie Hellman exchange in the Main Mode. The local entity selects the group specified by this object to perform Diffie Hellman exchange with the peer when this policy item is chosen to negotiate the Main Mode with an IKE peer.

hh3chipsIsakmpPolLifetime.name: hh3chipsIsakmpPolLifetime
hh3chipsIsakmpPolLifetime.description: This object indicates the lifetime of the IKE tunnels in seconds.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTable.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTable
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTable.description: The table includes the list of the member cryptomaps of the cryptomap sets which are set on the specific entity.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapEntry.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapEntry
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapEntry.description: Each entry contains properites of a single static cryptomap entry. The members of dynamic cryptomap sets, which may be linked with the parent static cryptomap set, are not included in this table.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapName.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapName
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapName.description: The name of the cryptomap entry in the cryptomap set. This is the first index component of this table.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapSN.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapSN
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapSN.description: The sequence number of the cryptomap entry in the cryptomap set. This is the second index component of this table.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapNegMode.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapNegMode
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapNegMode.description: Type of the cryptomap entry. This object may be an ISAKMP cryptomap or manual.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapMatchAddr.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapMatchAddr
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapMatchAddr.description: The access list number entered by the operatoir while creating this cryptomap.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapPeerIpAddr.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapPeerIpAddr
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapPeerIpAddr.description: The IP address of the current peer. Traffic protected by this cryptomap is protected by a tunnel terminating at the device whose IP address is the value of this object.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTransforName.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTransforName
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapTransforName.description: The transform associated with this cryptomap entry.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifetime.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifetime
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifetime.description: This object indicates the lifetime of the IPSec SA which is created using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifesize.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifesize
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLifesize.description: This object identifies the lifesize of the IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. Lifesize means maximum traffic in bytes that may be carried.

hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLocalIpAddr.name: hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLocalIpAddr
hh3chipsStaticCryptomapLocalIpAddr.description: The value of this object is the local IP address of the IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsIfNameUsed.name: hh3chipsIfNameUsed
hh3chipsIfNameUsed.description: This object indicates the name of the interface which uses this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsInAHSPI.name: hh3chipsInAHSPI
hh3chipsInAHSPI.description: This object indicates the inbound AH SPI IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsInESPSPI.name: hh3chipsInESPSPI
hh3chipsInESPSPI.description: This object indicates the inbound ESP SPI IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsOutAHSPI.name: hh3chipsOutAHSPI
hh3chipsOutAHSPI.description: This object indicates the outbound AH SPI IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsOutESPSPI.name: hh3chipsOutESPSPI
hh3chipsOutESPSPI.description: This object indicates the outbound ESP SPI IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsInAhHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsInAhHexKeyString
hh3chipsInAhHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the inbound AH authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The AH authentication key is in hex.

hh3chipsInEspCipherHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsInEspCipherHexKeyString
hh3chipsInEspCipherHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the inbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The ESP authentication key is hex.

hh3chipsInEspAuthenHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsInEspAuthenHexKeyString
hh3chipsInEspAuthenHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the inbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The ESP authentication key is hex.

hh3chipsInAhStringKeyString.name: hh3chipsInAhStringKeyString
hh3chipsInAhStringKeyString.description: This object indicates the inbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in string.

hh3chipsInEspStringKeyString.name: hh3chipsInEspStringKeyString
hh3chipsInEspStringKeyString.description: This object indicates the inbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in string.

hh3chipsOutAhHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsOutAhHexKeyString
hh3chipsOutAhHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the outbound AH authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in hex.

hh3chipsOutEspCipherHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsOutEspCipherHexKeyString
hh3chipsOutEspCipherHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the outbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in hex.

hh3chipsOutEspAuthenHexKeyString.name: hh3chipsOutEspAuthenHexKeyString
hh3chipsOutEspAuthenHexKeyString.description: This object indicates the outbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in hex.

hh3chipsOutAhStringKeyString.name: hh3chipsOutAhStringKeyString
hh3chipsOutAhStringKeyString.description: This object indicates the outbound AH authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in string.

hh3chipsOutEspStringKeyString.name: hh3chipsOutEspStringKeyString
hh3chipsOutEspStringKeyString.description: This object indicates the outbound ESP authentication key IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry. The key is in string.

hh3chipsTransformNameSetEntry.name: hh3chipsTransformNameSetEntry
hh3chipsTransformNameSetEntry.description: Each entry refers to properties of a transform.

hh3chipsIsCardTransform.name: hh3chipsIsCardTransform
hh3chipsIsCardTransform.description: This object indicates the flag of the NDEC is used for IPSec SAs generated using this IPSec policy entry.

hh3chipsInByte.description: Total bytes of the NDEC sent.

hh3chipsOutByte.name: hh3chipsOutByte
hh3chipsOutByte.description: Total bytes of the NDEC sent.

hh3chipsCardOperate.name: hh3chipsCardOperate
hh3chipsCardOperate.description: The version of the NDEC's CPLD. cardClearStatic(1): clear the statistics of the card cardReset(2): rest the card cardSynTime(3): synchoronize the clock of the card cardSysLogOn(4):turn on the log of the card cardSysLogOff(5):turn off the log of the card cardSysLogClear(6):clear the log of the card

hh3chipsNDECConnections.name: hh3chipsNDECConnections
hh3chipsNDECConnections.description: Total connections of the system at this time.

hh3chipsNDECBackup.description: The flag that NDEC using backup. The value 1 represents using backup The value 0 represents not using backup

hh3chipsNDECStateChangeTrap.name: hh3chipsNDECStateChangeTrap
